
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>SocialNetwork</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url("~/../../Images/fondo.jpg");
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        .contenedor {
            position: fixed;
            top: 45%;
            left: 37%;
            background: #2cabb2;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 2em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        select {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            height: 34px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.42857143;
            color: #555;
            background-color: #fff;
            background-image: none;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: inset 0 1px 1px rgba(0,0,0,.075);
        }

        .boton {
            background: #000;
            color: #fff;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.42857143;
            text-align: center;
            white-space: nowrap;
            vertical-align: middle;
            cursor: pointer;
            user-select: none;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="contenedor">
        <p>Selecciona la red social con que trabajarás.</p>
        <p>
            @{var listItems = new List<SelectListItem>
            {
              new SelectListItem { Text = "Twitter", Value="Twitter" },
            };
            }
            @Html.DropDownList("Exemplo", new SelectList(listItems, "Value", "Text"))
        </p>
        <input type="button" class="boton" value="Some text" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("FollowersCount", "Home")'" />
    </div>
</body>
</html>
